text: Baytimirovo () is a rural locality (a village) in Urshakbashkaramalinsky Selsoviet, Miyakinsky District, Bashkortostan, Russia. The population was 140 as of 2010. There are 2 streets. == Geography == It is located 19 km from Kirgiz-Miyaki, 11 km from Urshakbashkaramaly. == References == Category:Rural localities in Miyakinsky District
title: Baytimirovo
